collection.name: Relics Pass
collection.description:
The Relics Pass is brought to you by Jeff Cole and Mark Brazil, co-founders of **IKONICK** and **Metarelics**. 

Holding a Relics Pass will grant you one free mint and one discounted mint to Sneaks of Nature, a franchise from the mind of Cole. (http://www.sneaksofnature.xyz)

Freaks Find a Way this Summer. 

**Relic Reserves**: 1000 piece collections that are created or curated by Jeff Cole, provided to our Relics Pass holders twice yearly for free or at a highly discounted price. 

First collection: *Relic Punks*. 
Price: Free Mint.
Date: April 15th-20th, 2022. 

Verify your pass in Discord to check out the Relic Room, attend a Speaker Series from iconic entrepreneurs, thought leaders and entertainers, or just hang with the crew. Be sure to select your favorite pop-tart flavor on the way in. 

Cole - http://www.instagram.com/cole/?hl=en

IKONICK - http://ikonick.com

Metarelics - http://www.metarelics.co (50% off for Relics Pass Holders)
